Content: To get this started: In Germany, many local agencies have developed online processes to obtain birth certificates. Content:

I think this is a field underrepresented on HN, but with quite significant effects, e.g. for entrepreneurs that have to deal with bureaucracy.

Author: donavanm
Content:
Lets put some math on the network costs. An oft quoted cost is $1/mb at p95 for decent transit. 1 mbs * 2,592,000 seconds = 2,592,000 mb per month, / (8 * 1024 gigabytes) = 316GB transferred per month. Dividing our $1 / 316GB = $0.0031 per GB transferred _at a constant 1mbs_.
